                      <p>&#160;</p>

                      <p><strong>Why</strong>: so we can get to know you better; make our communications with you more personal; get in touch on your birthday; make sure we are not marketing/selling to children; learn and improve from your survey feedback, organise in store events and pick competition winners</p>

                      <p>&#160;</p>

                      <p><strong>Where</strong>: from you, your social media account provider and student body, such as Unidays</p>

                      <p>&#160;</p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>

                  <tr>
                    <td width="16%">
                      <p>Observed information</p>
