                      <p>&#160;</p>

                      <p><strong>Why</strong>: so our website and app technology can work properly with your device and make sure you can see and use our intended website and apps on the device you are using</p>

                      <p>&#160;</p>

                      <p><strong>Where</strong>: from you; from our website/app technology interaction with your browser/devices</p>

                      <p>&#160;</p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>

