                        <li>Klarna if you choose to use their payment service.</li>
                      </ul>

                      <p>Their privacy policies apply to their use of your details.</p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>

                  <tr>
                    <td width="151">
                      <p>Event, discount registration and account providers</p>
                    </td>

