                      <p>If we agree that we should stop that use of your personal information, or in limited other cases, the limitation will become permanent.</p>

                      <p>The impact of the restriction is limited to personal information affected by the request/use.</p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>

                  <tr>
                    <td width="26%">
                      <p><strong>Right to erasure</strong></p>
                    </td>

